	  <concept id="i1099478"
            ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3"
            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">19.1406</ph> Sole source awards to service-disabled veteran-owned small business concerns.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d1245e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1259e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            A contracting officer shall consider a contract award to a SDVOSB concern on a sole source basis (see <xref href="FAR-i6_302-5.dita#i6_302-5"
                        base="i1119624"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">6.302-5</xref>(b)(6)), before considering small business set-asides (see <xref href="FAR-i1101696.dita#i1101696"
                        base="i1101696"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.203</xref> and subpart <xref href="FAR-i1100723.dita#i1100723"
                        base="i1100723"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.5</xref>) provided none of the exclusions of <xref href="FAR-i1099419.dita#i1099419"
                        base="i1099419"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.1404</xref> apply and-</p>
					          <ol id="d1245e35" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1259e39" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The contracting officer does not have a reasonable expectation that offers would be received from two or more service-disabled veteran-owned small business concerns;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1259e48" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The anticipated award price of the contract, including options, will not exceed-</p>
							              <ol id="d1245e54" class="- topic/ol ">
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d1259e58" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    $6.5 million for a requirement within the NAICS codes for manufacturing; or</p>
								                </li>
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d1259e67" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    $4 million for a requirement within any other NAICS code;</p>
								                </li>
							              </ol>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1259e78" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The requirement is not currently being performed by an 8(a) participant under the provisions of <xref href="FAR-i1099848.dita#i1099848"
                              base="i1099848"
                              outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                              class="- topic/xref ">subpart  19.8</xref> or has been accepted as a requirement by SBA under <xref href="FAR-i1099848.dita#i1099848"
                              base="i1099848"
                              outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                              class="- topic/xref ">subpart  19.8</xref>;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1259e93" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The service-disabled veteran-owned small business concern has been determined to be a responsible contractor with respect to performance; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1259e102" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(5)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Award can be made at a fair and reasonable price.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1259e113" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The SBA has the right to appeal the contracting officer’s decision not to make a service-disabled veteran-owned small business sole source award.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
		    </conbody>
